#### CERTIFICATE UNLOCK LOGIC (Critical Rule)

🔒 A participant's certificate download is LOCKED until BOTH conditions are met:
  1. Registration status = Confirmed (payment approved if paid event)
  2. Post-event review form submitted

Lock states shown to student:
  → "Complete the feedback form to unlock your certificate"
  → "Your registration is pending payment approval"
  → "Certificate not yet published by the organizer"

Once BOTH conditions are met AND admin has synced the certificate:
  - Download button is UNLOCKED in student portal
  - Student receives automated email: "Your certificate is ready to download!"
  - Clicking download → backend verifies ownership → redirects to Drive URL
  - Direct Drive link is NEVER exposed to frontend (always proxied via backend)
    to prevent students from sharing/accessing others' certificates

